---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Torres Criminal Defense Grew to $112K Monthly Case Value" description="A Calgary criminal defense lawyer transformed lead response with 24/7 automation.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/legal-services/criminal-defense" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Criminal Defense Law
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Torres Criminal Defense Grew to $112K Monthly Case Value
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Calgary criminal defense lawyer transformed lead response with 24/7 automation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">91%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Lead Response Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">58%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Retainer Conversion</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">3.2x</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">More Referrals</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$112K</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Monthly Case Value</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Firm:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Torres Criminal Defense</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Calgary, AB</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Practice:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Criminal defense</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Focus:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">DUI, assault, drug charges</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Daniel Torres was losing leads to competitors. People arrested at night called other lawyers who answered. Clients and families called constantly with anxiety. Reviews were rare due to case sensitivity. Referrals were inconsistent.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented 24/7 automated lead response with urgent escalation, stage-based educational content to reduce anxiety, proactive case updates, and private referral requests respecting confidentiality.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Lead response rate hit 91%. Retainer conversion reached 58%. Referrals increased 3.2x. Monthly case value grew to $112K. Clients feel supported even when Daniel is in court.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "I used to lose half my overnight leads to faster-responding competitors. Now I capture them all, and they're already educated about their case when we meet."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">â€” Daniel Torres, Founder</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Capture More Cases?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-amber-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
